Description: 
    Provides tools for variable selection in high-dimensional regression models using the 
    generalized information criterion ('GIC') combined with 'Hopfield' network optimization. 
    The package supports a variety of generalized linear models ('GLMs'), including the 
    'Normal' and 'Poisson' families. Performance-critical components are implemented in 
    'Julia', while providing a user-friendly interface through 'R'. The package supports 
    optional 'Julia' setup and includes examples and vignettes. 'GLM' stands for 
    generalized linear model.
